generated_description: liberros is a company based in soest, utrecht, specializing in equine-assisted coaching. the company offers coaching sessions that combine traditional coaching methods with interactions with horses to provide insights into unconscious patterns and behaviors. liberros' approach aims to help individuals improve their work and personal situations, reduce stress, and enhance energy levels. the coaching sessions are conducted by an equine assisted coach who has completed a level 1 and 2 training program accredited by the dutch association of coaches (nobco) and the european accreditation of the international equine assisted coaching organization (eia).
